            <div corresp="#c5816f2">
                <head>Persia.</head>
                <p>Copley Amory, Jr. took over the Legation from Wallace D. Murray June 80, 1925,
                    pending the arrival of Stoffman Philips, formerly appointed minister.</p>
                <p>Hugh Millard, 2.2.0. class 6, detailed to Dept. of State, temporarily, for period
                    Oct. 10 to 19, 1929 inc, before proceeding to Teheran under assignment, of June
                    13, 1929.</p>
            </div>
